description: When GCD( p(n), q(n) ) increases, where p() is the unrestricted partition function (A000041) and q is the distinct partition function (A000009).
mathematica: a = 0; Do[ d = GCD[ PartitionsP[ n ], PartitionsQ[ n ]]; If[ d > a, a = d; Print[ n ]], {n, 1, 11050} ]
author: _Robert G. Wilson v_, Apr 23 2001
